You can rule a line across the page by typing four or more dashes.  In PikiPiki the number of dashes in a horizontal rule markup determine how thick it is: use them in moderation.  (A suggestion from John Farrell.)

no rule

---

thin rule
----
rule
-----
thick rule
------
really thick rule
-------

{{{

This does not apply in pre-formatted "verbatim" mode:

---
----
-----
------
-------

}}}